body_html:
Ad Blocker can cause "No data found" problem
I just want to add, that I had the problem that the TensorBoard wasn't showing any data although the log_dir was set correctly. The problem seemed to be the AdBlock plugin, that blocked specific content from being transfered. I add localhost to the AdBlock whitelist. Now its showing everything correctly.

body:
**Ad Blocker can cause "No data found" problem**
I just want to add, that I had the problem that the TensorBoard wasn't showing any data although the log_dir was set correctly. The problem seemed to be the AdBlock plugin, that blocked specific content from being transfered. I add localhost to the AdBlock whitelist. Now its showing everything correctly.
